title: Did Bayden give Gitmo prisoners 19 before the Americans?
subtitle: Dosis was first sent to the naval base at Guantánamo Bay before being deployed to facilities throughout the military compound.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: The President of the United States, Joe Biden, has developed a plan to provide CAVID-19 vaccines to detainees at the Guantanamo Bay prison camp in Cuba before many Americans receive their first dose.
